       Carneiro, 28-Nov-2013.) $)
    fbdmn0 $p |- ( F e. fBas -> X =/= (/) ) $=
      ( vx cfbas wcel c0 wn wne 0nelfb wceq wa cv wi wex wal cuni wral eqeq1i
