  ${
    $d x y z A $.  $d x y z B $.  $d x y z F $.
    $( A filter base contains subsets of its pairwise intersections.
       (Contributed by Jeff Hankins, 1-Sep-2009.) $)
    fbasssin $p |- ( ( F e. fBas /\ A e. F /\ B e. F ) -> E. x e. F x C_ ( A
    i^i B ) ) $=
      ( vy vz cfbas wcel cv cin wss wrex wral wa c0 wne wnel w3a isfbas2 ibi
      simp3d wceq ineq1 sseq2d rexbidv ineq2 rcla42v syl5com 3impib ) DGHZBDHZC
      DHZAIZBCJZKZADLZUJUMEIZFIZJZKZADLZFDMEDMZUKULNUPUJDOPZODQZVBUJVCVDVBREFAG
